y).<BR>* To install DirectX 8.1 drivers, click Yes to proceed, then follow the on-screen instructions. <BR><BR>7. When setup is complete, click <B>Yes</B> to reboot your computer. <BR><BR>8. Congratulations! You're now ready to play EverQuest ...<BR>* To connect and begin playing, double-click the EverQuest desktop icon. <BR><BR>

	
